name: Corbins of the Crystallized Sail
description: Hailing from the Rootmason capital city of Thespin, the Corbins of the Crystallized Sail are known for their adept handling of dune surfers. Now, blessed with a sundew lotus due to their ties with the Groodu, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
